Package RestaurantSim

Class RestaurantGuest

java.lang.Object
RestaurantSim.RestaurantGuest
All Implemented Interfaces:
ITickableActionObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
Customer, Sanepid
public abstract class RestaurantGuest
extends java.lang.Object
implements ITickableActionObject
Objects that extend this class can interact with a Restaurant. This class mimics the real world person that can come into a restaurant.
